template:
Crie um server block Nginx para reverse proxy.

Dominio: {{domain}}
Porta upstream: {{upstream_port}}
SSL: {{ssl}}

Inclua:
- proxy_pass para 127.0.0.1:{{upstream_port}}
- proxy_set_header (Host, X-Real-IP, X-Forwarded-For, X-Forwarded-Proto)
- Rate limiting (limit_req_zone)
- Gzip on
- Security headers (X-Frame-Options, X-Content-Type-Options, HSTS)
- Se SSL: TLS 1.2+, certificado Let's Encrypt, redirect HTTP->HTTPS
- Access log e error log separados

Gere uma commit message seguindo Conventional Commits.

Type: {{type}}
Scope: {{scope}}
Description: {{description}}

Formato: {{type}}({{scope}}): {{description}}

Regras:
- Em ingles
- Primeira linha: max 72 caracteres
- Imperativo (add, fix, update — nao added, fixed, updated)
- Sem ponto final
- Body opcional: explique WHY, nao WHAT
